snippet.title: Vampire Hunters Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Create absurd builds by stacking up weapons and raining down crazy firepower on vampires and demons in this rogue-lite retro FPS. Can you be know as the most outrageous Vampire Hunter in all of Transylvania?

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2206270/Vampire_Hunters/
